  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="11820746">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Quantum_Panda/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1033190-17.jpg" alt="陈朝" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11820746/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11820746/" class="">第267页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Quantum_Panda/" class=" " title="陈朝">陈朝</a>
                (曾用名量子熊猫)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11820746">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class=""> a = b

a^2 = ab

a^2 + a^2 -2ab = ab + a^2 - 2ab

2(a^2 - ab) = a^2 - ab

2 = 1

a = b 啊，a^2-ab＝0
两次同除以0，坑爹啊。作者以此指出，很多证明在最基本的问题上就犯下重大错误。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11820746/">(<span class="">6回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-03-13 17:21</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                 a = b<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>a^2 = ab<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>a^2 + a^2 -2ab = ab + a^2 - 2ab<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2(a^2 - ab) = a^2 - ab<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>2 = 1<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>a = b 啊，a^2-ab＝0<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>两次同除以0，坑爹啊。作者以此指出，很多证明在最基本的问题上就犯下重大错误。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







